            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300 mt-1">
              Autonomous email reading and Discord routing using Python and CrewAI.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="group">
          <a href="https://github.com/ezradante/dantes-item-forge" class="block hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
